title: Sjan van Dijk
text: Sjan van Dijk (born 4 February 1964) is a Dutch <a href="archery">archer</a>. She competed in the women's <a href="Archery%20at%20the%201992%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20individual">individual</a> and <a href="Archery%20at%20the%201992%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20team">team</a> events at the <a href="1992%20Summer%20Olympics">1992 Summer Olympics</a>.
